rdana,Arial&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Backend development experience (e.g., Golang, Ruby on Rails, Laravel, Express.js, django)</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Experience with CI/CI (Github workflow, Circle CI) and infrastructure (AWS, Heroku)</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">N3+ Japanese language</span></li></ul>', '["4"]', '11/12/2021', 'Thỏa thuận', 5, 'Tuyển dụng IT support', '["2"]', '["6","8"]', 2, NULL, '2021-11-30 16:12:15', '2021-11-30 16:12:15'),
	(3, '<ul style="padding-left: 2rem; color: rgb(57, 62, 70); font-family: &quot;Roboto,Helvetica,Verdana,Arial&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Analyze requirements, come up with the adequate technical design and maintain technical documentation</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Write clean and maintainable code using engineering best practices (unit testing, source control, continuous integration, design patterns, etc.). Comply with the coding standards (SDLC guidelines).</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Develop a mobile app base on our eCommerce platform.</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Collaborate closely with Project Manager and other team members to raise up suggestions or any concerns; actively suggest a plan of actions to improve overall quality.</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Troubleshoot performance, scale, object clustering issue for integration solutions and debugging.</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Research new technologies and existing libraries</span></li></ul>', '<ul style="padding-left: 2rem; color: rgb(57, 62, 70); font-family: &quot;Roboto,Helvetica,Verdana,Arial&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">At least 3 years of experience in iOS</span></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font